        ORDER BY o_orderpriority;

          AND l_shipdate > DATE '1998-09-30'

        ORDER BY revenue DESC, o_orderdate LIMIT 10;

        ORDER BY revenue DESC, o_orderdate LIMIT 10;

query_text:
-- Query 170
SELECT n_name, sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue
        FROM customer, orders, lineitem, supplier, nation, region
        WHERE c_custkey = o_custkey AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey AND l_suppkey = s_suppkey
          AND c_nationkey = s_nationkey AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey
          AND r_name = 'AFRICA' AND o_orderdate >= DATE '1998-07-08'
          AND o_orderdate < DATE '1999-07-08'
        GROUP BY n_name ORDER BY revenue DESC;

-- Query 171
SELECT n_name, sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue
        FROM customer, orders, lineitem, supplier, nation, region
        WHERE c_custkey = o_custkey AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey AND l_suppkey = s_suppkey
          AND c_nationkey = s_nationkey AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey
          AND r_name = 'AMERICA' AND o_orderdate >= DATE '1998-06-15'
          AND o_orderdate < DATE '1999-06-15'
        GROUP BY n_name ORDER BY revenue DESC;

query_text:
-- Query 172
SELECT
          c_custkey, c_name, c_acctbal, n_name, c_address, c_phone, c_comment
        FROM customer, nation, region
        WHERE c_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey
          AND r_name = 'EUROPE' AND c_acctbal > 2288
          AND c_mktsegment = 'MACHINERY'
        ORDER BY c_acctbal DESC LIMIT 20;

        FROM customer, orders, lineitem
        WHERE c_mktsegment = 'MACHINERY' AND c_custkey = o_custkey AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey
          AND o_orderdate < DATE '1998-09-22'
          AND l_shipdate > DATE '1998-09-22'
        GROUP BY l_orderkey, o_orderdate, o_shippriority
        ORDER BY revenue DESC, o_orderdate LIMIT 10;

-- Query 195
SELECT n_name, sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue
        FROM customer, orders, lineitem, supplier, nation, region
        WHERE c_custkey = o_custkey AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey AND l_suppkey = s_suppkey
          AND c_nationkey = s_nationkey AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey
          AND r_name = 'AFRICA' AND o_orderdate >= DATE '1998-06-08'
          AND o_orderdate < DATE '1999-06-08'
        GROUP BY n_name ORDER BY revenue DESC;

query_text:
-- Query 198
SELECT n_name, sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue
        FROM customer, orders, lineitem, supplier, nation, region
        WHERE c_custkey = o_custkey AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey AND l_suppkey = s_suppkey
          AND c_nationkey = s_nationkey AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey
          AND r_name = 'AFRICA' AND o_orderdate >= DATE '1998-10-01'
          AND o_orderdate < DATE '1999-10-01'
        GROUP BY n_name ORDER BY revenue DESC;

-- Query 202
SELECT
          c_custkey, c_name, c_acctbal, n_name, c_address, c_phone, c_comment
        FROM customer, nation, region
        WHERE c_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey
          AND r_name = 'AMERICA' AND c_acctbal > 3440
          AND c_mktsegment = 'FURNITURE'
        ORDER BY c_acctbal DESC LIMIT 20;

-- Query 212
SELECT n_name, sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue
        FROM customer, orders, lineitem, supplier, nation, region
        WHERE c_custkey = o_custkey AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey AND l_suppkey = s_suppkey
          AND c_nationkey = s_nationkey AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey
          AND r_name = 'ASIA' AND o_orderdate >= DATE '1998-07-23'
          AND o_orderdate < DATE '1999-07-23'
        GROUP BY n_name ORDER BY revenue DESC;

SELECT
          c_custkey, c_name, c_acctbal, n_name, c_address, c_phone, c_comment
        FROM customer, nation, region
        WHERE c_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey
          AND r_name = 'AMERICA' AND c_acctbal > 1805
          AND c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE'
        ORDER BY c_acctbal DESC LIMIT 20;

        FROM customer, orders, lineitem, supplier, nation, region
        WHERE c_custkey = o_custkey AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey AND l_suppkey = s_suppkey
          AND c_nationkey = s_nationkey AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey
          AND r_name = 'AMERICA' AND o_orderdate >= DATE '1998-09-16'
          AND o_orderdate < DATE '1999-09-16'
        GROUP BY n_name ORDER BY revenue DESC;

          AND o_orderdate < DATE '1999-07-01'
        GROUP BY n_name ORDER BY revenue DESC;

        GROUP BY o_orderpriority
        ORDER BY o_orderpriority;

-- Query 59
SELECT l_orderkey, sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue, o_orderdate, o_shippriority
        FROM customer, orders, lineitem
        WHERE c_mktsegment = 'FURNITURE' AND c_custkey = o_custkey AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey
          AND o_orderdate < DATE '1998-10-04'
          AND l_shipdate > DATE '1998-10-04'
        GROUP BY l_orderkey, o_orderdate, o_shippriority
        ORDER BY revenue DESC, o_orderdate LIMIT 10;

-- Query 73

        FROM customer, orders, lineitem
        WHERE c_mktsegment = 'HOUSEHOLD' AND c_custkey = o_custkey AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey
          AND o_orderdate < DATE '1998-06-24'
          AND l_shipdate > DATE '1998-06-24'
        GROUP BY l_orderkey, o_orderdate, o_shippriority
        ORDER BY revenue DESC, o_orderdate LIMIT 10;

        WHERE p_partkey = ps_partkey AND s_suppkey = ps_suppkey AND p_size IN (39,28,33,15,49)
          AND p_type LIKE '%BRASS' AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey
          AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey AND r_name = 'AFRICA'
        ORDER BY s_acctbal DESC, n_name, s_name, p_partkey LIMIT 100;

query_text:
-- Query 87
SELECT n_name, sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS revenue
        FROM customer, orders, lineitem, supplier, nation, region
        WHERE c_custkey = o_custkey AND l_orderkey = o_orderkey AND l_suppkey = s_suppkey
          AND c_nationkey = s_nationkey AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey
          AND r_name = 'ASIA' AND o_orderdate >= DATE '1998-09-30'
          AND o_orderdate < DATE '1999-09-30'
        GROUP BY n_name ORDER BY revenue DESC;

          c_custkey, c_name, c_acctbal, n_name, c_address, c_phone, c_comment
        FROM customer, nation, region
        WHERE c_nationkey = n_nationkey AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey
          AND r_name = 'ASIA' AND c_acctbal > 4122
          AND c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE'
        ORDER BY c_acctbal DESC LIMIT 20;

        FROM part, supplier, partsupp, nation, region
        WHERE p_partkey = ps_partkey AND s_suppkey = ps_suppkey AND p_size IN (19,40,33,43,12)
          AND p_type LIKE '%STEEL' AND s_nationkey = n_nationkey
          AND n_regionkey = r_regionkey AND r_name = 'EUROPE'
        ORDER BY s_acctbal DESC, n_name, s_name, p_partkey LIMIT 100;
